先装cuda

下载
https://developer.download.nvidia.com/compute/cuda/11.7.0/local_installers/cuda-repo-rhel7-11-7-local-11.7.0_515.43.04-1.x86_64.rpm

检查 
nvcc -V



再装 驱动 

去网页手动下载

再安装 py3

如果只安装了py3.6


就下载这个 


https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cu113/torch-1.10.2%2Bcu113-cp36-cp36m-linux_x86_64.whl


sudo python3.6 -m pip install torch...whl

检查

python3.6
import torch
print(torch.cuda.is_available())
